      "content": "the house is just so quiet now. it's like the silence is actually heavy, you know? i walk into the kitchen to make coffee and i just stare at his empty chair for like twenty minutes. i dont even know why i bother making it. everything just feels so pointless without him. i'm just a ghost wandering around a life that doesnt belong to me anymore.",
